short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Stops you from having an awkward one on one

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have a group call coming up? Do you hate getting to a meeting late but dont like the awkwardness of being on the call with just one other person?
Unmeet is just the chrome extension you need. We care about you, and never want you to be in a situation where you'll have to make small talk about Jennifer's stupid little cat.
